{"lemma":"رُتُجُ","slug":"رُتُجُ","root":"ر.ت.ج","root_slug":"ر-ت-ج","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-ت-ج","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n14673","n14676"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%8F%D8%AA%D9%8F%D8%AC%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n14673","headword_ar":"رَتَجَ","root":"rtj","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ratojN","text_ar":"رَتْجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 4.       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ratija","text_ar":"رَتِجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ratija fiY manoTiqahi","text_ar":"رَتِجَ فِى مَنْطِقَهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ratajN","text_ar":"رَتَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, impeded in his speech, unable to speak,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tonguetied;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, * Msb, K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^urotija","text_ar":"اُرْتِجَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Elyh","text_ar":"عليه"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aurotutija","text_ar":"اُرْتُتِجَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Elyh","text_ar":"عليه"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ausoturotija","text_ar":"اُسْتُرْتِجَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY AlqaAriY'i","text_ar":"عَلَى القَارِىءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^urotija","text_ar":"اُرْتِجَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ElY AlxaTiybi","text_ar":"على الخَطِيبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The reader,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reciter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the orator,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"preacher,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was unable to read,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"recite,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb,) as though he were prevented doing so, (Msb,) or as though a thing were closed against him like as a door is closed; (S;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, impeded in his reading,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"recitation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his oration,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sermon, and unable to complete it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh;) from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arotaja AlbaAba","text_ar":"اَرْتَجَ البَابَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh, Msb: [see 4:]) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aurotutija","text_ar":"اُرْتُتِجَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same: (S: [in my copy of the Msb, “"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Artyj","text_ar":"ارتيج"},{"kind":"text","text":", of the same measure as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aqtyl","text_ar":"اقتيل"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the pass. form: ” but this is evidently a mistranscription, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aurotutija","text_ar":"اُرْتُتِجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of the same measure as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Auqotutila","text_ar":"اُقْتُتِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) one should not say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aurotuj~a Elyh","text_ar":"اُرْتُجَّ عليه"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S: [but it seems that those who pronounced the verb with teshdeed said"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Airotaj~a","text_ar":"اِرْتَجَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rj","text_ar":"رج"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) this is sometimes said; but some disallow it: (Msb:) the vulgar say it; and accord. to some, it may be correct as meaning “ he fell into confusion. ” (Mgh.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaEida Alminobara faA^urotijaEalaY","text_ar":"صَعِدَ المِنْبَرَ فَاُرْتِجَعَلَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ascended the pulpit, and was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, impeded in his speech, unable to speak,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tonguetied."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY fulaAnK","text_ar":"عَلَى فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^urotija","text_ar":"اُرْتِجَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one was unable to finish a saying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"poetry, that he desired to utter."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY kalaAmihi ratajN","text_ar":"فِى كَلَامِهِ رَتَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In his speech is a reiterating, by reason of an impediment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inability to say what he would."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rataja","text_ar":"رَتَجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ratajAnN","text_ar":"رَتَجانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a child)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"walked a little, at his first beginning to walk;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"walked with a weak gait; crept along;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"walked slowly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","S","A","Msb","TA","Mgh"]},{"entry_id":"n14676","headword_ar":"رَتَجٌ","root":"rtj","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}